Qxc3 Rg5 {Grau plays an enterprising line of the Cambridge Springs.} 16. f3 b5
$5 {He tries to win and leaves his usual solid approach.} (16... Be6 {
occurred in Euwe - Bogoljubow, Netherlands 1928 (8).}) 17. Rad1 $1 bxc4 18.
Bxc4 $1 Qe5 $1 19. f4 {White threatens material.} Rxg2+ $1 20. Kxg2 Qe4+ $2 {
