{Preparations for the international tournament Mar del Plata 1963 were started,
but the event did not occur, because the sponsorship by the casinos and
lotteries stopped. It could be resumed in 1965, when the government took over
the financial support. Thereafter, the closed international tourney became
irregular. Sometimes a Latin-American event took place. An open tournament
began in 1967 and it continued annually until the present.   Twelve rounds of
the twenty-sixth Mar del Plata event were played at Hotel Nogaro. The
remaining three rounds happened at the Jockey Club in La Plata. The event
lasted from 19 iii until 8 iv 1965. Special guests were Stein, Averbakh, Pal
