Qe7 24. Qd4 Qf6 {Otherwise he cannot stop the attack.} 25. Qxf6 gxf6 26. Nd4
Re8 27. Re3 Rb8 $6 {Exchange prolongs the game.} 28. b3 b5 29. cxb5 Bxb5 30.
